r />\r\n算了，浪费时间<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n说点别的吧<br />\r\n<div class=\"reply_wrap\">他可以控诉山田尚子强烈的个人执念所构建的结局让他作为观众的体验感受很差</div><br />\n这句话是什么意思 ","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"1826","username":"凛凛233","adminid":"0","groupid":"32","memberstatus":"0","number":"1825","dbdateline":"1545392452","groupiconid":"8"},{"pid":"42022745","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"astrayveller","authorid":"505868","dateline":"2018-12-21 19:47","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=42014620&amp;ptid=1795203\"><font color=\"#999999\">星野航 发表于 2018-12-21 08:03</font></a><br />\n多说一嘴好了(希望砖楼里大家别嫌我烦）<br />\r\n作者构造人物的途径是从原型--事实，这种模式是先验的，而对于观众 ...</div><br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 你搞错了一个重点 如果说电影里还允许演员的即兴演出 动画这方面可操作的空间就非常小了。同一个角色的不同镜头肯定是多个原画二原动画合力完成的，某个人瞬间的灵感在全篇里实现非常困难。而且电影可以拍摄再剪辑，动画这么做消耗太大。所以我认为山田对每个镜头的强力控制是必要的。动用原画画无意义的镜头那是在浪费<br />\n&nbsp; 再说，那些强调演出的镜头也没有张扬到影响理解画面和人物关系上，我觉得这已经比较克制了<br />\n<br />\n— from Xiaomi MI 8 UD, Android 8.1.0 of <a href=\"https://pan.baidu.com/s/1mi43uRm\">S1 Next Goose</a> v2.1.2","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"8","replycredit":"0","position":"1827","username":"astrayveller","adminid":"0","groupid":"52","memberstatus":"0","number":"1826","dbdateline":"1545392842","groupiconid":"10"},{"pid":"42022760","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"yone0000","authorid":"154038","dateline":"2018-12-21 19:48","message":"回头去看第一季的时候发现，希美坐的这个地方，就是第一季第十集里丽奈说对老师不是like是love的地方嘛<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/068.png\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/large/bfae17b6ly1fyelvy4egtj20ua0gbkhm.jpg\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/large/bfae17b6ly1fyelwcbmglj20tw0gp1kx.jpg\" /></div><br />\r\n","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"1828","username":"yone0000","adminid":"0","groupid":"54","membersta